      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I've truly babied it since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with that 'new car' feel still totally intact. Seriously, you won't find a single flaw on this one! If you're looking for perfection, you've found it. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
