    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level BMW E46 M3, a definitive analogue masterpiece. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized volumetric efficiency across the rev range. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: rod bearings and subframe reinforcement have been completed to factory standards. The suspension geometry remains taut, utilizing OEM components to preserve the original handling dynamics. With flawless paint depth and a pristine cabin, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning collector.",
